content.detailedDescription: My family and our friends were camping in the sierra nevada mountains.  on the night of july 4th, several of us stayed up to watch the stars.  we noticed multiple satellites (craft that look like stars crossing fairly regularly on the same path at roughly the same speed, through the night sky with no flashing or blinking lights).  the satellites did not mean much to us until we saw one quite nearly do a 90 degree turn and then disappear.  we also saw what looked like a satellite traveling due east.  suddenly a much faster object, also looking like a satellite, came toward it at a high rate of speed, heading west.  these objects were so far away they only appeared as moving stars.  as the faster object approached from the east, the slower object from the west appeared to make an abrupt turn to the left, heading north, away from the oncoming, faster object.  when they came near each other, both flashed and disappeared.  after that, we saw dark spaces in the night sky that would suddenly have a bright blast of light and then go completely dark again.  sometimes the objects would blink multiple times, almost rhythmically.  other times the lights would flash just once or twice then stop.  we saw these flashing star like lights in numerous places in the sky throughout the night.  we also saw two very fast moving aircraft, flying very high and very fast approach from the west.  both had flashing/blinking/aircraft lights.  the first air craft split hard and went north east and over the mountain ridges towards the area where the two satellite looking lights had nearly intercepted each other then disappeared just minutes earlier.  the 2nd aircraft continued on a straight line north west over the mountain range, towards the direction the one satellite looking object turned towards before it disappeared.  not one single commercial aircraft we saw that night, out of the dozens we saw, took the same flight path as those two fast moving aircraft i just described.
content.summary: Bright flashes, directional changes, aircraft redirect

content.detailedDescription:
I actually happened to be temporally rooming with a friend at the time that is only a couple blocks away from where a lot of my experiences take place. her house is very old and has dark paneled walls and covered windows so the house is always quite dark even during the day, extremely by night. i had my own room while i stayed there, but do to my fear of darkness and issues with sleep, i always slept in the same bed as my roommate and dear friend. she has always been sympathetic to my nighttime issues. on this particular night i decided not to sleep with her and instead slept across the room on a futon.

i always kept the tv on as a light source while i lay down for the evening. the tv has a timer and turns itself off during the night. i constantly get up at night so i always keep a flashlight on me. from the bedroom the bathroom is a very short, but very dark distance.

after going to sleep i remember waking in a groggy state only to realized i was weightless and slowly being pulled upward and i was outside. my first intuitive reaction was roll over, but i stopped immediately for the fear if i began to move like that, i would fall from whatever was lifting me. it was at that moment i realized what was happening was familiar and i knew i just needed to go with the flow. first visuals that i remember seeing is turning my head to my right and seeing the neighborhood and trees below. this is when that fear of i better not turn i could fall. i was extremely high up. i had to be under the clouds of course, but this distance is one of 20 stories... not sure. im still being pulled slowly upward on my back when i then turned my head to left. i only remember blackness, just black to left. thats when i looked directly above me and the object that was pulling me was now only some feet away and this is when i noticed detail. i could not tell you how big it was, but i remember it felt huge and the edges were not in my site. in was dark, there were no lights that i remember and no sound that i recall. i felt as if it was a large round disk, because there were lines that came out from the edges and met in middle of the disk, but right before all the lines met up in middle, they stopped at a circle right in the middle. only example i can think to give you at moment would be a simple drawing like one a child would make of a sun with the rays extending outward, of course without the crudeness of children's drawing.
that when i closed my eyes. maybe i fell back asleep, not sure. next i remember standing in the middle a large room. it was all white i think and very brightly lit. straight across from me was a counter that resembled a curved bar like one that would be in hospital were a receptionist would sit behind while she checked in patients. there were no beings in my view. the room looked empty, but i felt a few presences. though i couldn't see anyone, i knew and i could feel them there. so i immediately and demandly spoke to them. and it was something to the tune of.... "ok, lets do this. all i ask you is please do scare me, dont make me fearful" i guess it is here that i should state that i was extremely tired, or groggy. kinda the same feeling i have when i wake up in the middle of sleepwalking. it was dreamlike, but not quite. now as far as the rest of my experience on this craft or place i was at, i don't have any recollection. but i went on to dream and woke up out of this dream before dawn,

the dream consisted of being at my grandfathers house out in the country where i grew up at. it is the only place on earth i ever felt safe and it was my home. but in this dream, i remember looking through the back sliding glass door into the face of what i would consider a gentle soft featured gray alien that almost seemed pleasant and cute. then to the right of this sliding glass door (lets say the door looked out north) is a smaller window that had little sheers over it (and this window looked out east. as i approached this window and opened the sheers, i looked straight into the face of another gray alien. but this one was different. it had harsh features, more defined lines on its face, look menacing, hideous and dark. its features were defined and angled while the features of first were soft and smooth. thats when i awoke. i tried to chalk off the night as a dream. i told my friend about it, she said she woke up in the middle of the night, looked over across the room where i had decided to sleep for the night and she said i was not there. she noticed the bedroom door was still closed which made here wonder. when i get up at night i always leave the bedroom door open, use my flashlight to get bathrrom where i turn on that light. then run back. she said she just passed back out and didnt think again of it. to make myself feel better. i told my friend i was gonna go outside and look for evidence of the encounter i new wouldnt be there. low and behold i found some. i cried. the entire roof of where i stayed was covered in leaves. thick layer of leaves and what i could only assume would be old dirt or mildew that looked black in color on the shingles, except for one area. right above where i slept that night it was completely free of leaves and it was alot lighter than rest, as if someone took a pressure washer and cleaned that small area of roof above where i slept.
content.summary: Levitated to dark craft extremely high above home. seen bottom of craft, next in white round empty room.

content.detailedDescription:
My husband and i were sitting on sunset beach, nc 8:50 pm july 3, 2016 waiting for fireworks to start in distance on ocean isle beach, nc. at 9 pm fireworks began and kind of disappointingly looked pretty far away from our vantage point. these are southern facing beaches so we were seated facing more easterly to observe fireworks. we both noticed what we thought a small plane at first in distance as it was moving very slowly in our direction.. thinking whoever it was had great front row seat observing fireworks from air. 
  as it turned out we ended up watching this "plane" as much as the fireworks, cause there was just something about it that didn't seem exactly right.. kinda glancing equally back and forth at this plane, then the fireworks. not too many other people on beach except for big family with kids and they were in front of us just watching in direction of fireworks and jumping around. no one else seemed to notice this thing or mentioned it as they were all intent on looking at fireworks. 
  well next the distant fireworks took total back seat to us as we became much more interested in this object. which was obviously not a plane as we had originally thought.. as it moved closer to our location. it was fairly high up but we quickly determined that it definitely wasn't a plane.. could plainly see that. it moved extremely slowly and then became apparent as a reddish orange glowing object and we both said what the heck is that?? no plane could stay in air moving that slowly and there was no engine sound of any kind.. totally silent, and no actual lights as you would see on a plane.. just a combination sphere-starlike solid reddish orange glowing brightness. we had never seen anything like that before and could not take our eyes off of it.
   let us be perfectly clear...This was not a fireworks! it was a very bright object moving in a straight path from ocean isle beach to sunset beach a bit back from the beach coastline... not over ocean. it then hovered in place high above but practically right over us, and we thought maybe a drone? it moved side to side and back and forth a bit but mainly hovered in place. then all of a sudden it moved backwards and just seemed to hyperspace away quickly into the clouds! the way it backed up and vanished is beyond what any helicopter could do.. and like i said we heard absolutely no sound from it!!  never imagined anything could move that fast.. like an instantaneous reverse disappearance.  never saw it after that remained on beach awhile longer in hopes it would reappear but did not. now cant stop thinking about it. unfortunately did not get any photos. we contacted our son who is a pilot to tell him what we saw and he did not think from our description it would be a drone, or a plane which would have blinking lights.
content.summary: Bright orange-red object moving slowly northeast to northwest over sunset beach, nc coastline

in the army. that left me disabled. after all of this i have come to the only truth i can. the why. and the answer is. i don't know. but i can live with the only truth i will ever know. and that truth is. i was taken by something and someone for a period of time in 1963 in houston texas. i still don't know if anyone will understand . perhaps it was just my 3 year old mind playing tricks on me back then. who knows.Just thought i would let someone know. please don't judge me.

content.detailedDescription:
I was walking on the beach a little after 10pm on 24 april 2016 when i noticed a red light that was stationary in the sky.  i watched it for a few seconds to see if it was a military or civilian aircraft but i didn't see the flashing lights you normally see on the wing tips and underside.
there was no sound that i could hear from a helicopter or a plane.  

i was standing about 100 meters or so on the west side of the hrbt and the object appeared to be above the bridge itself at about 70 degrees or so.  it was approx the size of a small tablet like a baby aspirin.  after a few seconds, i  pulled out my phone to take a video.   i ended up with two clips as the light on the camera came on and i had to turn it off and try to film again.  

after i restarted the camera with the flash off, the object began to slowly move in a n direction but disappeared from my view when it appeared to be obscured by clouds but hard to say as it was dark out and the lights from the hrbt itself are very bright.  i did manage to zoom in on the object as it was moving away before i lost it.  

no idea what it was.   i have lived in the area for more than 20 years and spent much of that in the military.   i am familiar with most of the aircraft we normally see in the area, military, civil and civilian.


the video file names are the time-stamps of when the video was taken.
content.summary: I was on the beach when i observed a silent red light hovering in the sky that slowly moved north.

content.detailedDescription:
Este testimonio es de terceras personas, relatado por un ex compañero policía en actividad
policiales recibieron un testimonio del familiar del dueño de una estancia cercana a río gallegos al mediodía del 2/7/16, al lugar concurrió un oficial de civil con el familiar para tomar conocimiento de lo ocurrido.
esa madrugada se escucharon sonidos y vieron luces en un corral de la estancia, el sueño pensando que eran cuatreros salió armado junto con dos de sus empleados y vieron movimiento en el corral y la ruta de acceso a unos 200 metros de distancia, lugar al que dispararon repetidas veces con fusiles.
los testigos aseguran que se vieron entidades que no eran humanas.
las luces se apagaron y luego un objeto brillante salió hacia arriba, cuando se acercaron al corral encontraron ovejas mutiladas, y cuando se hizo de día encontraron pisadas extrañas y marcas en un corral aledaño.
al llegar al lugar pasado el mediodía ya estaban trabajando en el corral un grupo de personas y el área estaba demarcada con cinta de peligro.
no se permitió hablar con el dueño del campo y se prohibió el acceso al área porque se dijo que se trataba de una enfermedad de las ovejas llamada de la lengua azul que se desconoce si se contagia a las personas, pero se pudo ver que a los animales les faltaban miembros como los ojos genitales.
estaban en el lugar varios vehículos de color blanco que el día 7/7/16 se vieron en caravana entrando a una estancia cercana a la ciudad de comandante luis piedra buena unos 200 km más al norte.
no se realizó reporte de policía.
content.summary: Avistaje y mutilación ganado cerca de guer aike - río gallegos

content.summary: I was meditating in my truck outside of town in the country to make contact with et beings and was asking for a sign that i was being heard  when 10 very small mettalic balls embedded themselves into my windshield in a very tight small pattern
